    "SUMMARY": "The 2024–25 F.C. Copenhagen season is the club's 33rd season in existence, all of which have been competed in the top flight of Danish football. In addition to the domestic league, Copenhagen will compete in this season's edition of the Danish Cup and, by virtue of winning the 2023–24 Danish Superliga European Playoff, is competing in the UEFA Conference League. The season covers the period from 1 July 2023 to 30 June 2024.\n\n"
